title: June 21, 2016 - A new study came out and it found the best state to grow up in is Minnesota. The study was conducted by researchers who have never been to California, Hawaii, Alaska, North Carolina, Arizona, Colorado, Montana, Vermont, Virginia, New Hampshire, Utah, Connecticut, Delaware, Maine, Massachusetts, and New York.
